  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is taken in the bright dining room and is buffet style with homemade pastries, eggs, cold meats and cheeses all served with freshly-brewed coffees and teas.</p>
<p>The hotel's <span>à</span> la carte restaurant is known for its food. They have fresh fish dishes and home-made pizza, pasta, risotto and delicious desserts. During summer, take advantage of the warm weather and eat on the terrace overlooking the lake. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
