  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel's in the perfect location in the centre of Desenzano. It's right in front of the ferry stop, close to bars, shops and restaurants, and around a 15-minute walk from the station. It's steeped in history and has been managed by the Mayer family for seven generations. Join them for a drink on the fantastic terrace that overlooks the lake.</p>]]></listingDescription>
