  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are finished in light colours and can sleep up to two people. They have side lake views from the balcony and facilities include air conditioning, TV, safe, minibar, hairdryer and shower.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> sleep up to three people and enjoy stunning lake views from the balcony (extra bed is a single bed). They have a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> can sleep two people and have a living area and balcony or terrace with lake views.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
